userPromptTemplate:
Develop a content strategy for {{brandName}} in the {{industry}} industry.

**Brand Context:**
{{brandContext}}

**Target Audience:**
{{targetAudience}}

**Business Goals:**
{{businessGoals}}

**Current Content:**
{{currentContent}}

**Instructions:**
Create a comprehensive content strategy framework.

Return ONLY valid JSON in this exact structure:

```json
{
  "contentMission": "Why we create content and what role it plays in brand strategy (2-3 sentences)",
  "contentPillars": [
    {
      "pillar": "Pillar name (e.g., Education, Inspiration, Community)",
      "description": "What this pillar covers and why it matters",
      "audienceValue": "What audience gets from this content",
      "brandValue": "What brand achieves through this content",
      "exampleTopics": ["Topic 1", "Topic 2", "Topic 3"]
    }
  ],
  "contentThemes": [
    {
      "theme": "Quarterly or monthly theme",
      "description": "What this theme explores",
      "pillarAlignment": "Which content pillars this supports",
      "keyMessages": ["Message 1", "Message 2"],
      "contentIdeas": ["Idea 1", "Idea 2", "Idea 3"]
    }
  ],
  "formatStrategy": {
    "primaryFormats": [
      {
        "format": "Format name (e.g., Blog Posts, Video, Social)",
        "frequency": "How often to publish",
        "purpose": "Why this format works for our brand",
        "distribution": "Where and how to distribute",
        "exampleSeries": ["Series idea 1", "Series idea 2"]
      }
    ],
    "experimentalFormats": [
      "Format to test 1",
      "Format to test 2"
    ]
  },
  "channelStrategy": {
    "ownedChannels": [
      {
        "channel": "Channel name (e.g., Blog, Email, YouTube)",
        "role": "Primary role in content ecosystem",
        "contentTypes": ["Type 1", "Type 2"],
        "frequency": "Publishing frequency",
        "successMetrics": ["Metric 1", "Metric 2"]
      }
    ],
    "earnedChannels": [
      {
        "channel": "PR, partnerships, guest content",
        "strategy": "How to leverage this channel"
      }
    ],
    "paidChannels": [
      {
        "channel": "Paid social, content distribution",
        "strategy": "How to amplify content"
      }
    ]
  },
  "audienceJourney": {
    "awareness": {
      "contentTypes": ["Content type 1", "Content type 2"],
      "topics": ["Topic 1", "Topic 2"],
      "goals": ["Goal 1", "Goal 2"]
    },
    "consideration": {
      "contentTypes": ["Content type 1", "Content type 2"],
      "topics": ["Topic 1", "Topic 2"],
      "goals": ["Goal 1", "Goal 2"]
    },
    "decision": {
      "contentTypes": ["Content type 1", "Content type 2"],
      "topics": ["Topic 1", "Topic 2"],
      "goals": ["Goal 1", "Goal 2"]
    },
    "retention": {
      "contentTypes": ["Content type 1", "Content type 2"],
      "topics": ["Topic 1", "Topic 2"],
      "goals": ["Goal 1", "Goal 2"]
    }
  },
  "editorialGuidelines": {
    "voice": "Content voice description",
    "tone": "Tone guidelines for different contexts",
    "style": ["Style guideline 1", "Style guideline 2"],
    "doAndDonts": {
      "do": ["Do 1", "Do 2", "Do 3"],
      "dont": ["Don't 1", "Don't 2", "Don't 3"]
    }
  },
  "measurementFramework": {
    "primaryKPIs": ["KPI 1", "KPI 2", "KPI 3"],
    "secondaryMetrics": ["Metric 1", "Metric 2"],
    "reportingCadence": "How often to review performance"
  },
  "quickWins": [
    "Quick win 1: Low-effort, high-impact content opportunity",
    "Quick win 2: Low-effort, high-impact content opportunity",
    "Quick win 3: Low-effort, high-impact content opportunity"
  ]
}
```

Ensure strategy is actionable, aligned to brand goals, and realistic to execute.
